<p><strong>Itinerary</strong></p>
<p><strong>DAY 1 WEDNESDAY</strong><br />Transfer by coach from the airport to the Hotel Barchetta in Como.</p>
<p><strong>DAYS 2-3 THURSDAY/FRIDAY</strong><br />Free days to explore the city of Como. Visit the amazing Gothic Cathedral, explore the city and enjoy its many restaurants and bars. Take a train to busy, bustling Milan or take a boat trip on the lake to one of the nearby resorts.</p>
<p><strong>DAY 4 SATURDAY<br /></strong>Transfer by ferry from the ferry terminal close to your hotel in Como and disembark in Menaggio right beside the Grand Hotel Menaggio where you will stay for 7 nights.</p>
<p><strong>DAY 5 SUNDAY</strong><br />Your first day in Menaggio where you can relax and enjoy getting to know the local area.</p>
<p><strong>DAY 6 MONDAY</strong><br /><strong>St Moritz and the Bernina Express Excursion</strong> - travel to Switzerland for a memorable day to glitzy St Moritz and the wonderful Bernina Express train ride from Poschiavo.</p>
<p><strong><strong>DAYS 7-8 TUESDAY/WEDNESDAY  </strong></strong>Free days to explore Lake Como - take a ferry ride to picturesque Bellagio, visit the famous Villa Carlotta which is in nearby Tremezzo or relax by the pool in your hotel.</p>
<p><strong>DAY 9<strong>THURSDAY</strong></strong><br />Bergamo Excursion - Enjoy a guided visit to one of Italy's most impressive medieval cities. The cost of the ferry ticket to the pick up point in Varenna is not included (approx. €8 return).</p>
<p><strong>DAY 10 FRIDAY<strong> </strong></strong><br />A final day to take in some sunshine and enjoy the beautiful lake.</p>
<p><strong>DAY 11 SATURDAY</strong><br />A final day to take in some sunshine and enjoy the beautiful lake.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div> </div>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><strong>What’s included</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Return flights to Milan from the UK on Wednesday, returning Saturday</li>
<li>Transfers by coach between the airport and your hotels</li>
<li>Transfers between Como and Menaggio</li>
<li>10 nights BB/HB accommodation in 4 star hotels</li>
<li>2 excursions </li>
<li>Assistance of Inghams Reps in Menaggio and telephone contact when in Como</li>
</ul>
<p>Please note that we act at all times as selling agent for the suppliers of activities &amp; excursions. See our <a data-udi="umb://document/b703ff07ccec43baad41fffcfcc61821" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b703ff07ccec43baad41fffcfcc61821}" title="Terms &amp; Conditions">terms &amp; conditions</a>.</p>
